moji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"夠多人清條撚咩<br />\n拎gear係為信心 有信心就會留 多人留就清唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"帶gear嘅 代表你有意志去抵抗<br />\n無帶gear嘅 代表根本無諗過 遇到衝突時 有抵抗嘅念頭<br />\n有幾多萬人都無用<br />\n當然其實有無帶gear 唔代表你係有無意志<br />\n只係正常有預計有衝突嘅人 點會唔帶野去保護自己<br />\n<br />\n&quot;人多就安全&quot; 係一個迷思<br />\n我部份認同<br />\n因為大部份人無意志抵抗 幾多萬都無用<br />\n個個望住前線被人拉走唔幫手<br />\n但係如果有意志抵抗 就算得一千幾百<br />\n拉住每個手足 可以甚至反擊 擊退攻勢<br />\n<br />\n所以如果決定留時<br />\n個人認為係要考慮有在場有意志嘅人 實質有幾多"},{"pid":"7f32872e08f9f448670feca00df1487afac41497","tid":1457171,"uid":17172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daa6db2c0ed826152c71cbba374ec8236703d188","tid":1457171,"uid":224731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"你估你d gear 可以頂到子彈?<br />\n冷靜d 啦, 帶左果d所謂gear 不死身咩<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日繼續入去接機啦 </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:13.000Z","msg":"總比裸裝食tg 擋子彈好<br />\n個重點 係個心理因素"},{"pid":"b8b18b489df7f424214ba8b71053827098ee72d4","tid":1457171,"uid":17172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"ebeca749adfeb00db37275426ce20880edb7f85c","tid":1457171,"uid":17172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"011d5fb5cf1772c5e7fd6b87720aaff7849f8648","tid":1457171,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"不割不篤不撤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cd65011df9524fee6d720228fe67b280b641c7","tid":1457171,"uid":259645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"做市民幾時都要企硬對付黑警，總之無委任證就無身分證！"},{"pid":"033db12b7bba2a6